    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>To provide a safer environment for individuals working on-site at the Federal University of Paran\u00e1, Curitiba, Brazil, we performed a large-scale mass testing SARS-CoV-2 program coupled with variant genotyping using two PCR-based approaches. We observed a fast dominance of the Gamma variant, displacing other variants in less than three months.</jats:p>\n                <jats:sec>\n                  <jats:title>Article Summary Line</jats:title>\n                  <jats:p>Coronavirus variants of concern may use asymptomatic population as silent spreaders to perform a fast displacement of previous established strains.</jats:p>\n                </jats:sec>",
